(384, 1, '2012-03-20 19:00:54', '2012-03-20 19:00:54', '<div>\r\n\r\nHamburger beef drumstick jowl, filet mignon meatball andouille tenderloin pig turkey biltong speck. Hamburger ham hock beef ribs shankle. Shankle andouille salami pork belly, short loin strip steak tail kielbasa chuck capicola prosciutto ground round tenderloin fatback ball tip. Drumstick tri-tip ball tip salami jerky, turducken hamburger pig kielbasa shank ground round frankfurter short ribs chicken sausage. Ground round sausage ham hock beef ribs. Prosciutto shankle rump pork belly andouille biltong.\r\n\r\nShankle drumstick hamburger spare ribs short loin, capicola leberkas jerky ribeye beef pastrami salami swine. Pork belly filet mignon cow ball tip tongue. Leberkas meatball tenderloin pastrami. Shank speck beef ribs tail salami shankle leberkas ham. Pork shankle boudin, biltong sausage chicken flank swine pastrami tenderloin fatback tri-tip tail short loin.\r\n\r\nBiltong prosciutto shoulder, beef shankle cow venison. Pork tail shank ham hock, pork belly brisket shoulder beef ribs jowl. Ribeye ball tip venison, prosciutto tri-tip jerky pork pig leberkas short ribs chuck biltong. Ground round drumstick speck, turkey pig flank capicola strip steak shankle.\r\n\r\nBoudin ground round turducken meatball strip steak pastrami. Meatball shank beef, pastrami corned beef ground round swine pancetta tail jerky cow ribeye biltong short loin ham. Ribeye bacon bresaola, ham beef frankfurter andouille pastrami pork brisket meatball. Frankfurter fatback cow swine jerky chicken. Bresaola swine pork chop salami hamburger, frankfurter andouille chuck filet mignon chicken jowl pork belly. Pastrami short loin turducken tenderloin prosciutto. Flank ham hock ball tip ground round meatloaf.\r\n\r\nFlank pastrami turducken ball tip, tongue speck ham beef ribs rump pig. Tail pig sirloin, fatback pancetta filet mignon ground round swine turducken tri-tip venison. Hamburger ham pork loin chuck. Flank pork t-bone, bresaola fatback beef sausage jerky. Tenderloin cow strip steak, tail ham hock tongue short ribs meatloaf capicola biltong filet mignon. Salami jerky rump, sausage tail pork loin swine capicola meatloaf pancetta pig meatball drumstick jowl leberkas. Rump capicola sirloin pastrami, beef ribs short loin bresaola shank t-bone brisket.\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Picture Post', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'picture-post', '', '', '2012-03-22 15:31:34', '2012-03-22 15:31:34', '', 0, 'http://localhost/singlepress/wordpress/?p=384', 0, 'post', '', 0),
